feat(security): perimeter sensor selection for armed_stay + ci/docs

Add user-selectable perimeter sensors for armed_stay (Skallsikring) mode
so internal motion can be ignored while doors/windows and outdoor sensors
remain active. Empty list keeps legacy behavior (all sensors active).

- lib/types.ts: add perimeter_sensors: string[] to GuardSettings
- lib/Capabilities.ts: new shared classifier with sensorType() and
  isVideo() that detects "soft cast" devices (Chromecast, Google Cast,
  Nest, Sonos, AirPlay) without cast_url capability
- api.ts /zones: return sensors[] per zone with id/name/type plus
  audio/video/light device name lists for UI badges
- app.ts: isPerimeterSensor() gate in onMotion/onContact when armed_stay
- settings/index.html: list sensors per zone with checkbox for
  Skallsikring; cap-badge tooltips show detected device names

Also:
- bump app version to 0.5.0 across app.json, .homeycompose/app.json,
  package.json
- add mode_changed trigger (mode_new, mode_previous tokens)
- add timestamp- add timestamp- add timestamp- add timestamp- add theckout@v5, setup- add timestamp- add timestamp- add timestamp- add timest README, in-app docs and spesification.md updated to reflect the new
  Skallsikring flow, cast detection, mode_changed and timestamp tokens
